channel.title: Server Won't Start
channel.description: Sever won't start. :S.... It keeps saying ------------------------------------------------- Note: stream.java uses or overrides a deprecated API. Note: Recompile with -Xlint:deprecation for details. Starting pimpscape Server on 0.0.0.0:43594 ---------------------------------------- Normally after that it retrieves some stuff from sugardaddy.dreamhost and a few other places and people can get on it. But now it isn't. I fixed it for a while earlier by editing a little bit in runserver.bat but then that shut down too. Please help me any info is greatly appreciated. Post here or add me on MSN Ironpyro@Hotmail.com Thanks in advance, King Pyro ( Foxes Buddy )
